<div class="wp-block-damndelicious-featured-comment">
	<h2>Featured Comment</h2>
	<div class="comment-content">Oh my goodness…how delicious is this?! I used my cast iron pan for both the salmon and the sauce. The salmon was beautiful – crispy on the outside and so moist inside. I doubled the sauce recipe and served it with Greek lemon rice. Restaurant worthy!</div>
