</div>
<p>Yummy! Didn&#8217;t have spinach,  used Chard instead.  Didn&#8217;t have fresh dill or lemon,  lol. Used fresh lemon balm instead.  No white wine either,  used more chicken broth.  Served with garden fresh oven roasted okra. It was delightful! Thanks for the recipe!</p>
</div>

