<p>Oh my goodness&#8230;how delicious is this?!  I used my cast iron pan for both the salmon and the sauce. The salmon was beautiful &#8211; crispy on the outside and so moist inside.  I doubled the sauce recipe and served it with Greek lemon rice.  Restaurant worthy!</p>
