<p>I have not made this yet…sounds very good and I will make it, but what’s the story with what pan to use?  You recommend a non-stick skillet and then in instructions you say to use a cast iron skillet?  So which one?  Think I’ll use the non-stick as I think the fish will stick to the cast iron, although I love cast iron or steel pans…</p>
