				<time pubdate datetime="2023-01-12T10:22:03-08:00">
				January 12, 2023 @ 10:22 AM				</time>

				<a rel="nofollow" class="comment-reply-link" href="#comment-289233" data-commentid="289233" data-postid="32293" data-belowelement="comment-289233" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Sharon" aria-label="Reply to Sharon">Reply</a>							</div><!-- .comment-meta -->


			<div class="comment-content"><p>I plan to make this tonight with some wild-caught coho salmon. One thing: recipe says to use a large cast iron skillet but your introductory comments “highly recommend” a non-stick pan. I’m going to use my well-seasoned black iron skillet. This looks delicious and healthy! Thanks.</p>
</div>

