</div>
<p>This is such a great recipe &#8211; I&#8217;ve made it a few times for my family, and it&#8217;s a hit. I don&#8217;t change anything, except that I add more spinach and more dill. Serve with roasted fingerling potatoes to soak uptake sauce (a nice loaf of crusty bread would work, too). Easy enough for weeknights, but nice enough for guests.</p>
</div>

